graph TD
    A[Customer Initiates Onboarding] --> B{Select Customer Type}
    B --> C[Individual Customer]
    B --> D[Business Customer]

    C --> E[Collect Individual Information <br/>- Name, Address, DOB, etc.]
    D --> F[Collect Business Information <br/>- Company Name, Address, TIN, etc.]
    F --> G[Identify Ultimate Beneficial Owners (UBOs)]
    G --> H[Collect UBO Information]

    E --> I{Document Collection}
    H --> I

    I --> J[Identity Proof <br/>- Passport, Driver's License]
    I --> K[Address Proof <br/>- Utility Bill, Bank Statement]
    I --> L[Financial Information <br/>- Source of Funds, Income Statement]

    J --> M{Identity Verification}
    K --> M
    L --> M

    M --> N[Verify Document Authenticity]
    N --> O{Is Document Valid?}
    O -- No --> P[Request for Additional/Valid Documents]
    P --> I
    O -- Yes --> Q[Screen against Sanctions/AML Lists <br/>- PEP, Adverse Media]

    Q --> R{Match Found?}
    R -- Yes --> S[Enhanced Due Diligence (EDD)]
    S --> T[Gather Additional Information <br/>- Source of Wealth, Nature of Business]
    T --> U[Manual Review by Compliance Team]
    U --> V{High Risk?}
    V -- Yes --> W[Reject Application]
    V -- No --> X[Conditional Approval]

    R -- No --> Y{Risk Profiling}

    Y --> Z[Analyze Customer Data <br/>- Occupation, Location, Transaction Patterns]
    Z --> AA{Assign Risk Level}
    AA --> AB[Low Risk]
    AA --> AC[Medium Risk]
    AA --> AD[High Risk]

    AD --> S
    AB --> AE{Decision}
    AC --> AE
    X --> AE

    AE -- Approve --> AF[Account Approved & Activated]
    AE -- Reject --> W
    X -- Conditions not Met --> W

    AF --> AG[Ongoing Monitoring]

    AG --> AH{Transaction Monitoring}
    AH -- Suspicious Activity --> AI[File Suspicious Activity Report (SAR)]
    AI --> AJ[Review and Update Risk Profile]
    AH -- No Suspicious Activity --> AG
    AG --> AK{Periodic Review}
    AK -- Change in Risk --> AJ
    AK -- No Change --> AG
end
